subject: Survey on software developers
msgSnippet: Hi, Freddy Munoz, a PhD working with me, has just ran a survey about developers and the first results have just come out. I hope you find it interesting.
messageBody:
Hi,

Freddy Munoz, a PhD working with me, has just ran a survey about developers and the first results have just come out. I hope you find it interesting. http://www.antelink.com/blog/software-developer-survey-first-chapter.html

You can also answer a new survey about software developers at http://survey.antelink.com/rollingSurvey or use this link to share it on social networks http://bit.ly/mRIBy1

Thanks for sharing :)

Michael Attia
